### Variables
@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000/api
@token = 

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Register New User
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "password_confirmation": "password123"
}

### Login (Copy token from response and paste above)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get Profile (Protected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Profile (Protected)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Updated"
}

### Change Password (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/change-password
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "current_password": "password123",
  "password": "newpassword123",
  "password_confirmation": "newpassword123"
}

### List All Locations (Protected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/locations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Location (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/locations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Location",
  "address": "Jakarta, Indonesia",
  "latitude": -6.2088,
  "longitude": 106.8456,
  "geofence_radius": 500,
  "notes": "Created via REST Client"
}

### Get Single Location (Protected) - Replace {id} with actual ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/locations/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Location (Protected) - Replace {id} with actual ID
PUT {{baseUrl}}/locations/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Location Name",
  "geofence_radius": 1000
}

### Delete Location (Protected) - Replace {id} with actual ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/locations/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Check Geofence (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/locations/check-geofence
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "latitude": -6.1944,
  "longitude": 106.8229
}

### Find Nearby Locations (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/locations/nearby
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "latitude": -6.2088,
  "longitude": 106.8456,
  "radius": 5000
}

### List All Reminders (Protected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reminders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List Active Reminders Only (Protected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reminders?active=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Reminder (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reminders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "location_id": 1,
  "title": "Test Reminder",
  "description": "Created via REST Client",
  "is_active": true
}

### Get Single Reminder (Protected) - Replace {id} with actual ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/reminders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Reminder (Protected) - Replace {id} with actual ID
PUT {{baseUrl}}/reminders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Reminder Title",
  "is_active": false
}

### Toggle Reminder Status (Protected) - Replace {id} with actual ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/reminders/1/toggle
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Trigger Reminder Manually (Protected) - Replace {id} with actual ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/reminders/1/trigger
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Active Reminders by Location (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reminders/active-by-location
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "latitude": -6.2088,
  "longitude": 106.8456
}

### Delete Reminder (Protected) - Replace {id} with actual ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/reminders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Logout (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Logout All Devices (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/logout-all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
